@baseUrl = http://localhost:5192
@token = 

### Step 1: Login as SuperAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@smallhr.com",
  "password": "SuperAdmin@123"
}

### Step 2: Get Token (copy from response above)
@token = <paste-token-here>

### Step 3: Test User Management Endpoint (Admin Endpoint - Query filters bypassed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/usermanagement/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 4: Test Admin Controller - Verify SuperAdmin
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/verify-superadmin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 5: Test Admin Controller - Get SuperAdmin Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/superadmin-users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 6: Test Tenants Endpoint (Admin Endpoint - Query filters bypassed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 7: Check Audit Logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/adminaudit?pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 8: Check Audit Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/adminaudit/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 9: Test Regular Endpoint - Employees (Query filters should NOT be bypassed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 10: Test Subscriptions Plans (Admin Endpoint)
